620
01:09:05,039 --> 01:09:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo mi na mišiće.

621
01:09:07,279 --> 01:09:08,720
[SPEAKER_01] Na tajnu naše dugovječnosti.

622
01:09:08,960 --> 01:09:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] Na tajnu dugovječnosti.

623
01:09:12,479 --> 01:09:15,039
