924
01:43:03,920 --> 01:43:06,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u realitetu to je deset puta manje.

925
01:43:06,880 --> 01:43:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mora biti pojedi kilu i pol sardina da dobiješ ti 5 grama kreatina.

926
01:43:11,680 --> 01:43:15,439
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, imaju sardine kreatin, ali ga nemaju toliko koliko je ovaj rekao.

927
01:43:15,680 --> 01:43:19,600
