960
01:47:02,000 --> 01:47:02,319
[SPEAKER_01] 3 mg.

961
01:47:03,359 --> 01:47:04,640
[SPEAKER_01] Za tebe prije je 4-5.

962
01:47:04,960 --> 01:47:05,439
[SPEAKER_00] 4-5.

963
